{"tid":1262853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊張既巴絲入黎放鬆下心情","createTime":"2019-06-28T01:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T01:53:30.000Z","uid":232082,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8309760d53640f20eb6d5a95f3aec0baa23f9c88","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:43:10.000Z","msg":"聽心經可以非常容易放鬆心情<br />\n我地打緊長期戰爭<br />\n精神狀態好緊要<br />\n要照顧好自己<br />\n<br />\n奉上 陳奕迅 －心經<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYf3MTpC6Zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoYf3MTpC6Zo&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=3e5a81e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYf3MTpC6Zo</a><br />\n<br />\n《般若波羅蜜多心經》<br />\n<br />\n觀自在菩薩，行深般若波羅蜜多時，照見五蘊皆空，度一切苦厄。<br />\n<br />\n舍利子！色不異空，空不異色；色卽是空，空卽是色，受想行識亦復如是。<br />\n<br />\n舍利子！是諸法空相，不生不滅，不垢不淨，不增不減。<br />\n<br />\n是故空中無色，無受想行識；無眼耳鼻舌身意；無色聲香味觸法；<br />\n<br />\n無眼界，乃至無意識界；無無明，亦無無明盡，乃至無老死，亦無老死盡；<br />\n<br />\n無苦集滅道；無智亦無得。以無所得故，菩提薩埵。<br />\n<br />\n依般若波羅蜜多故，心無罣礙；無罣礙故，無有恐怖，遠離顛倒夢想，究竟涅槃。<br />\n<br />\n三世諸佛，依般若波羅蜜多故，得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。<br />\n<br />\n故知般若波羅蜜多是大神咒，是大明咒，是無上咒，是無等等咒，能除一切苦，真實不虛。<br />\n<br />\n故說般若波羅蜜多咒。卽說咒曰：揭諦揭諦，波羅揭諦，波羅僧揭諦，菩提薩婆訶。"},{"pid":"e606ef47bccffcfa8626ff882d40ccf0fe000acc","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 深呼吸⋯⋯慢慢⋯⋯<br />\n1⋯⋯2⋯⋯3⋯⋯"},{"pid":"20c6e22bb755c43a6ac1eebfae81836372c159ac","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c126a835484b7e95a8fbc70c0a4519cde756e94e","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"記得每一日都要抖夠精神<br />\n身體壞左<br />\n好多野想做都未必做到"},{"pid":"351dd6e6b3a8abc2da33fb4964aefb5aadf3962e","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f06e31050fc2652249f8c7e57f773c20e3256d","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1b3ddd4e5ed09ebd53b2c972ac3a4a2451001d","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6546d5becdc420f2f42ba88a138b3925b12c7b1","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"31ce567dce4c2351a6911998fd0b2ec87b82f135","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"f9f2669308089a2f298c104797954b9960a214e3","tid":1262853,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"再推一下！"}]}